<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <header class="text-center py-12 mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
      <span class="text-gradient">United States of America</span>
      <span class="block text-americana-crimson mt-2">United</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-americana-textMuted max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
      An Alternate History of American Isolationism and Innovation
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/story/{{ storyGraph.startNode }}/" class="btn btn-primary text-lg">
        Begin Your Journey
      </a>
      <button
        @click="$store.story && $store.story.currentNode && (window.location.href = '/story/' + $store.story.currentNode + '/')"
        x-show="$store.story && $store.story.currentNode && $store.story.visitedNodes.length > 1"
        class="btn btn-outline text-lg"
      >
        Continue Story
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Story Overview -->
  <section class="card mb-12">
    <h2 class="card-header">The Premise</h2>
    <div class="prose-story">
      <p>
        <strong>1945.</strong> World War II ends. America stands alone as the world's superpower‚Äîthe only nuclear nation, the strongest economy, unmatched industrial might.
      </p>
      <p>
        In our timeline, America chose <strong>intervention</strong>. The Marshall Plan. NATO. Permanent overseas bases. Endless wars in Korea, Vietnam, Iraq, Afghanistan.
      </p>
      <p>
        But what if America had chosen <strong>differently</strong>?
      </p>
      <p>
        What if those resources‚Äîtrillions of dollars, millions of man-hours‚Äîhad turned <strong>inward</strong>? What if the Manhattan Project's brilliance kept flowing to civilian technology? What if immigration was strictly merit-based, limited to the world's best scientists and engineers?
      </p>
      <p class="text-americana-crimson font-bold text-lg">
        This is that story. A branching narrative where you explore alternate Americas, each shaped by choices at critical moments.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Stats -->
  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-12">
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-americana-gold mb-2">{{ storyGraph.stats.totalNodes }}</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-americana-textMuted">Story Nodes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-americana-crimson mb-2">{{ storyGraph.stats.decisions }}</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-americana-textMuted">Decision Points</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center">
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-americana-navy mb-2">{{ storyGraph.stats.endings }}</div>
      <div class="text-sm text-americana-textMuted">Possible Endings</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-center" x-data="{visited: $store.story ? $store.story.visitedNodes.length : 0}">
      <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-americana-text mb-2" x-text="visited"></div>
      <div class="text-sm text-americana-textMuted">Your Progress</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Paths -->
